text.section:
Each person who conducts auctions as a business in this State of motor vehicles of a type required to be registered under this article shall keep a record of:
The name and address of the consignor;
The date on which it was consigned;
The year, make, model, and serial number of each vehicle consigned;
The title number and state where the vehicle was last registered;
The odometer mileage reading at the time of consignment;
The name and address of the person to whom the vehicle was sold;
The selling price; and
The date of sale.
